I love JE boys!!!

I am from Singapore.
You can call me Sally.
I love making new friends. (:
I love Japan!!!
The culture, the place, the food, the weather and of course our pretty boys. (:
I enjoy watching Jdoramas (and cry to a lot of them) and occassionally, animes.
I can talk endlessly about HSJ, NewS, KAT-TUN, Arashi, Kanjani 8, Tackey & Tsubasa, Smap, V6, Ya-Ya-Yah, J.J. Express, Johnny Juniors, you name it!
I also listen to others which includes Ayumi Hamasaki, Koda Kumi, SPEED, Hello!Project, Noriko Sakai, Mr Children, and too many to name.

English, Korean and Chinese groups such as Panic! At the disco, Rascal Flatts, Neyo, SS501, FT. Island, CNBLUE,S.H.E, Jay Chou....... too.

But none of those beats my favourite JPOP. (sorry, biased.)
